<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            animation: shake 0.5s infinite;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0px #ff00ff, 7px 7px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transform: rotate(-3deg);
        }
        .grape {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            padding: 20px;
            animation: crazyRotate 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes crazyRotate {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg) scale(1); }
            25% { transform: rotate(90deg) scale(1.2); }
            50% { transform: rotate(180deg) scale(1); }
            75% { transform: rotate(270deg) scale(1.2); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg) scale(1); }
        }
        @keyframes shake {
            0% { transform: translate(1px, 1px) rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: translate(-1px, -2px) rotate(-1deg); }
            50% { transform: translate(-3px, 0px) rotate(1deg); }
            75% { transform: translate(3px, 2px) rotate(-1deg); }
            100% { transform: translate(1px, -1px) rotate(0deg); }
        }
        .description {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            animation: rainbow 3s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes rainbow {
            0% { color: #ff0000; }
            20% { color: #ffff00; }
            40% { color: #00ff00; }
            60% { color: #00ffff; }
            80% { color: #ff00ff; }
            100% { color: #ff0000; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <img src="/images/what.png" alt="Max" class="grape">
        <div class="description">
            <p>โอ้ มายก๊อด!!! นี่นายจะมาใช้ API ของฉันอย่างนั้นหรือ?</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>